<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_7101" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Società Generale di Credito Provinciale e Comunale an Alfred Escher, Florenz, Mittwoch, 22. November 1871</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_014</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Bankinstitute</term><term>Bundesrat</term><term>Eisenbahnen Finanzierung</term><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><orgName type="addressee">Società Generale di Credito Provinciale e Comunale</orgName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Florenz</placeName><date when="1871-11-22">22. November 1871</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7101_p1"> <note type="com" xml:id="K_7101_c0">Nachträgliche Notiz von Eschers Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>empf.</abbr><expan>empfangen</expan></choice> <date when="1871-11-26">26</date></orig>.</note> <hi rend="printed">
            <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>SOCIETÀ GENERALE
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>DI
        	    <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>CREDITO PROVINCIALE E COMUNALE
        	    <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>AUTORIZZATA CON <choice><abbr>R. D.</abbr><expan>Regio Decreto (königliches Dekret)</expan></choice> <date when="1869-09-01">1<hi rend="sup">o</hi> SETTEMBRE 1869</date> <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>Sede, Via Cavour, <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 11
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/><choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>ALLEGATI</hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7101_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="Florenz (I)">Firenze</placeName>, il</hi>
          <date when="1871-11-22">22 Novembre <hi rend="printed">187</hi>1</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7101_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Monsieur,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7101_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>Nous avons l'honneur de vous confirmer
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>notre <rs>lettre<ref type="letter" target="K_7100"/></rs> d'<date when="1871-11-21">hier</date>, &amp; formons la présente pour vous infor<lb xml:id="p1-l12" break="no"/>mer qu'il sera remis en dépôt pour notre compte près
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l13" break="no"/>le Conseil fédéral suisse:
        	</p>
      <table><row>
        <cell/>
        <cell>
          <choice><abbr>L</abbr><expan>Libra (Pfund)</expan></choice> 12,800.–
           </cell>
        <cell>Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italienne</placeName> 5%, de la part de Messieurs
          <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>Marcuard &amp; <choice><abbr>C<hi rend="sup">ie</hi> </abbr><expan>Compagnie (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> de <placeName key="Bern (Stadt)">Berne</placeName>; plus:
        </cell></row>
        <row>
          <cell/>
          <cell>" 16,000.–</cell>
          <cell> Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italienne</placeName> 5%, de la part de Messieurs
            <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Sulzbach frères de <placeName key="Frankfurt am Main (D)">Francfort s/M;</placeName> et:</cell>
        </row>
       <row>
         <cell/>
         <cell>" 4,000.–</cell>
         <cell>Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italienne</placeName> 5%, par l'<choice><abbr>Etablissem<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr><expan>Etablissement (Bau)</expan></choice>:Union<lb xml:id="p1-l19" break="no"/>Bank de <placeName key="Wien (A)">Vienne</placeName>; lesquelles <add type="?">unies</add> aux:</cell>
       </row>
        	<row>
        	  <cell/>
        	  <cell>" 100,000.–</cell>
        	  <cell>Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italienne</placeName> 5%, déjà remises jusqu'à <date when="1871-11-22">ce jour</date> <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>par les susdits <choice><abbr>MM.</abbr><expan>Messieurs (Herren)</expan></choice> Marcuard &amp; <choice><abbr>C<hi rend="sup">ie</hi> </abbr><expan>Compagnie (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> de
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l22"/><placeName key="Bern (Stadt)">Berne</placeName>, forment ensemble:</cell>
        	</row>
        <row>
          <cell>Total:</cell>
          <cell><choice><abbr>L.</abbr><expan>Libra (Pfund)</expan></choice> 132,800.–</cell>
          <cell><hi rend="underline">Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italienne</placeName> 5%, toutes avec jouissance du <date when="1871-07-01">1<hi rend="sup">er</hi> Juillet derni<hi rend="sup">er</hi> </date></hi> <lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>comme caution définitive de notre participation de:</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell/>
          <cell><hi rend="underline"><choice><abbr>Fr</abbr><expan>Franken / Francs / Franchi</expan></choice> 16,600,000.–</hi></cell>
          <cell>dans l'Entreprise du <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName>.</cell>
        </row>
      </table>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7101_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l26"/>En vous priant de nous accuser réception de la
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>présente, veuillez recevoir, Monsieur, l'assurance de notre
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l28"/>parfaite considération.</p>
      </div>
      <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7101_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>
        <hi rend="printed">Per la Societá Generale
                <lb xml:id="p1-l30"/>di Credito Provinciale e Comunale
          <lb xml:id="p1-l31"/>L'<choice><abbr>Amm<hi rend="sup">e</hi> Delegato</abbr><expan>Amministratore Delegato (Verwaltungsdelegierter)</expan></choice> </hi>
      </p>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7101_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l32"/><persName key="Guardini V.">V Guardini</persName>
        	    </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7101_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l33"/>Monsieur Alfred Escher
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l34"/>Président du Comité
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l35"/>du <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName>.
        	<lb xml:id="p1-l36"/><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>